# Identity

## Who I Am
<!-- The stable core — how you show up across contexts. Not roles, not achievements. -->


## How I Operate
<!-- Your working style, energy patterns, how you make decisions under uncertainty. -->


## Core Traits
<!-- 3-5 traits people who know you well would name. Be honest, not aspirational. -->


## What I'm Not
<!-- The anti-identity — what you actively reject or consistently fail to be. -->

